Kebbit teeth are dropped from Sabre-toothed kebbits after a successful deadfall trapping. The teeth can be used with a pestle and mortar to create Kebbit teeth dust, which is used to make a Hunter potion in the Herblore skill.

The Herblore Hunting potion info refers to Kebbit teeth dust as 'ground sabre-toothed Kebbit teeth'. These are the same item.

The Herblore Hunting potion info refers to Kebbit teeth dust as 'ground sabre-toothed Kebbit teeth'. These are the same item.
